thread.title: Arthur Finkler Freiberger
thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da Arthur Finkler Freiberger

author: Arthur Finkler Freiberger
title: Arthur Finkler Freiberger
text:
I am really happy with my experience with Otticanet. Once the item was shipped from Italy, it made me feel a little bit scared, but, the parcel got to Australia quite quickly! And the quality of the Oakley sunglasses I bought is just great!
Would definitely recommend, and if I ever need sunglasses again, will give otticanet a go again ;)
